// of a product based on the given context.
//
// Security measures implemented:
// 1. Sandboxed Lua environment - dangerous libraries removed
// 2. Execution timeout - prevents long-running scripts
// 3. Input validation - validates script before execution
func ExecutePricingScript(script string, ctx map[string]float64) (float64, error) {
